# Cloudflare Pages redirects
# Forces canonical host (non-www) and HTTPS.
#
# Do not add /page -> /page.html redirects here. Cloudflare Pages already
# redirects .html URLs to extensionless URLs, so reversing that creates an
# ERR_TOO_MANY_REDIRECTS loop.
# Format: <source>  <destination>  <status>

https://www.freedevtool.org/*    https://freedevtool.org/:splat    301!
http://freedevtool.org/*         https://freedevtool.org/:splat    301!
http://www.freedevtool.org/*     https://freedevtool.org/:splat    301!
